Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
create_property_alias(25.10)                      create_property_alias(25.10)

Name
       create_property_alias  -  Creates a property alias for the selected ob-
       jects

Syntax
       create_property_alias

        [-help]

       -map <alias_propery_name_pairs>

       -obj_type {pin port cell net clock lib_cell  lib_pin  design  lib  tim-
       ing_path  timing_point  timing_arc  path_group lib_timing_arc si_victim
       si_attacker lib_pg_pin pg_pin pg_net}

       Creates a property alias for the selected objects.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       -map <alias_propery_name_pairs>
              Specifies pair list of alias and property to be  associate  with
              that  alias,  such as, {alias1 prop1} or {{ialias1 prop1}{alias2
              prop2}...}.

       -obj_type {pin port cell net clock lib_cell lib_pin

              design lib timing_path timing_point timing_arc path_group

               lib_timing_arc si_victim si_attacker lib_pg_pin pg_pin pg_net}"
              Specifies the object type for which a property alias needs to be
              created.

